# CROSS-LANGUAGE CLI LIBRARY TAXONOMY — AXIS 44 CONTINUES:
#   DOCKER CLIENT / CONTAINER ORCHESTRATION (Go side)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# This completion **CONTINUES AXIS 44** in the cross-
# language CLI library taxonomy.  R765 Rust=99
# (dockrtui/bollard OPENS Axis 44) → R766 Go=99
# (dobi/fsouza/go-dockerclient CONTINUES Axis 44
